<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFCF6A70FCE997A41B2DB989" pageId="52" pageNumber="810" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFCF6A70FCE997A41B2DB989" blockId="52.[788,1382,395,818]" pageId="52" pageNumber="810">
Based on genetic data, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFCF6A70FB8697A41B65B92C" baseAuthorityName="Harrison" baseAuthorityYear="1979" box="[1146,1381,509,542]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Hypsugo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="52" pageNumber="810" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="arabicus">Hypsugo arabicus</taxonomicName>
appears to be sister to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFCF6A70FBB6947D1AB1B977" baseAuthorityName="Bonaparte" baseAuthorityYear="1837" box="[1098,1201,548,581]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Hypsugo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="52" pageNumber="810" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="savii">H. savii</taxonomicName>
, with 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFCF6A70FAFF947D1B66B977" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1904" box="[1283,1382,548,581]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Hypsugo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="52" pageNumber="810" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="ariel">H. ariel</taxonomicName>
basal to this clade. Often placed in 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFCF6A70FAE894121D58B9A6" authorityName="Kaup" authorityYear="1829" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Pipistrellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="52" pageNumber="810" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Pipistrellus</taxonomicName>
, but genetic data unequivocally situate this species in 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFCF6A70FBEE94C31A81B989" box="[1042,1153,666,699]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Hypsugo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="52" pageNumber="810" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Hypsugo</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFCF6A70FCE894981AFFB9D0" box="[788,1279,705,738]" pageId="52" pageNumber="810" type="distribution">
<caption id="90EB6676FFCF6A70FCE894981AFFB9D0" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6397972" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6397972" box="[788,1279,705,738]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6397972/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="52" pageNumber="810" targetBox="[173,764,403,816]" targetPageId="52">
