Benda, Al-Jumaily et al. (2011), Benda, 
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFFCF6A70FD039E921D57B3D6" box="[767,855,2251,2276]" country="Saint Vincent and the Grenadines" name="Saint Andrew" pageId="52" pageNumber="810">Andreas</collectingRegion>
&amp; Reiter (2002), Benda, Faizolahi et al. (2012), Benda, Reiter et al. (2016), Harrison (1979, 1982), Harrison &amp; Bates (1991), Tsytsulina (2008b).
